  },
  {
    title: 'Gutter Repair',
    body: 'Loose gutters, leaking joints, sagging sections, improper slope — we repair all of it. If your gutters are salvageable, we\'ll fix them without upselling you on a full replacement you don\'t need.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.42 15.17L17.25 21A2.652 2.652 0 0021 17.25l-5.877-5.877M11.42 15.17l2.496-3.03c.317-.384.74-.626 1.208-.766M11.42 15.17l-4.655 5.653a2.548 2.548 0 11-3.586-3.586l6.837-5.63m5.108-.233c.55-.164 1.163-.188 1.743-.14a4.5 4.5 0 004.486-6.336l-3.276 3.277a3.004 3.004 0 01-2.25-2.25l3.276-3.276a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.336 4.486c.091 1.076-.071 2.264-.904 2.95l-.102.085m-1.745 1.437L5.909 7.5H4.5L2.25 3.75l1.5-1.5L7.5 4.5v1.409l4.26 4.26m-1.745 1.437l1.745-1.437m6.615 8.206L15.75 15.75M4.867 19.125h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Gutter Guard Installation',
    body: 'Gutter guards keep leaves, debris, and shingle grit out of your gutters so they keep flowing without constant cleaning. We install quality gutter guard systems that actually work in the Texas climate.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Downspout Repair & Replacement',
    body: 'A gutter system is only as good as its downspouts. We inspect, repair, and replace downspouts as part of any gutter service.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Gutter Cleaning & Maintenance',
    body: 'Clogged gutters back water up under your shingles and overflow onto your foundation. We clean and flush gutter systems to restore proper flow.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"/></svg>`,
  },
];

const whyCards = [
  {
    title: 'Honest Assessment First',
    body: "We don't push replacement if repair will do the job. After a thorough assessment, we'll recommend the most cost-effective solution for your gutters.",
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 8.25h9m-9 3H12m-9.75 1.51c0 1.6 1.123 2.994 2.707 3.227 1.129.166 2.27.293 3.423.379.35.026.67.21.865.501L12 21l2.755-4.133a1.14 1.14 0 01.865-.501 48.172 48.172 0 003.423-.379c1.584-.233 2.707-1.626 2.707-3.228V6.741c0-1.602-1.123-2.995-2.707-3.228A48.394 48.394 0 0012 3c-2.392 0-4.744.175-7.043.513C3.373 3.746 2.25 5.14 2.25 6.741v6.018z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Seamless & Sectional Options',
    body: 'We install both seamless and sectional gutter systems in a range of materials so you get the right fit for your home and budget.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 6.75h12M8.25 12h12m-12 5.25h12M3.75 6.75h.007v.008H3.75V6.75zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zM3.75 12h.007v.008H3.75V12zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0zm-.375 5.25h.007v.008H3.75v-.008zm.375 0a.375.375 0 11-.75 0 .375.375 0 01.75 0z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Gutter Guards Available',
    body: 'Want gutters you don\'t have to clean every season? We install gutter guard systems that keep debris out and water flowing.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Full System Approach',
    body: 'Gutters, downspouts, slope, drainage — we look at the whole system, not just the section that\'s obviously failing.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 010-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.964-7.178z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: 'Roofing + Gutters Under One Roof',
    body: 'When you\'re replacing a roof, new gutters often make sense at the same time. Lone Ranger handles both — one contractor, one call, one project.',
    icon: `<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 12l8.954-8.955c.44-.439 1.152-.439 1.591 0L21.75 12M4.5 9.75v10.125c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125H9.75v-4.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21h4.125c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V9.75M8.25 21h8.25"/></svg>`,
