---

<MainLayout
  title="Gutter Installation & Repair in Temple, Killeen & Central Texas | Lone Ranger Roofing"
  description="Lone Ranger Roofing installs seamless and sectional gutters, performs gutter repairs, and installs gutter guards across Temple, Killeen, and Central Texas. Free estimate."
  darkHero={true}
>

  <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[65vh] flex items-center bg-brand-900 overflow-hidden -mt-28">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/gutter-hero.webp"
        alt="Gutter installation and repair — Temple and Killeen TX"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-900 via-brand-900/85 to-brand-900/30"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 pt-20 pb-28">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Residential Services</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white leading-tight mb-6">
          Gutter Installation &amp; Repair in Temple, Killeen &amp; Central Texas
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Gutters are the superheroes of your home — quietly directing rainwater away from your foundation, siding, and landscaping every time it rains. When they fail, your home pays for it.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/contact" class="bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white font-black px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center shadow-lg">
            Get a Free Gutter Estimate
          </a>
          <a href="tel:+12543001413" class="border-2 border-white/50 hover:border-white text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-sm uppercase tracking-wide transition-colors text-center hover:bg-white/10">
            Call (254) 300-1413
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-3 mt-10">
          {[
            'Seamless & Sectional',
            'Repair Before Replace',
            'Gutter Guards Available',
          ].map(t => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gold-400 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              {t}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== WHY GUTTERS MATTER ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-6xl mx-auto">

        <div>
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">WHY GUTTERS MATTER</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6">
            What Happens When Your Gutters Fail in Central Texas
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Central Texas doesn't get gentle rain. When it rains here, it dumps — and without properly installed, properly functioning gutters, that water goes exactly where you don't want it. Foundation erosion, siding rot, basement water intrusion, landscape destruction, and fascia damage are all common results of gutter systems that are failing, clogged, improperly sloped, or just not there.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Lone Ranger Roofing installs and repairs gutter systems for homeowners across Temple, Killeen, Harker Heights, Belton, Salado, Georgetown, and throughout DFW. We don't believe in sales drama — if your gutters can be repaired, we'll repair them. If they need replacing, we'll tell you why and give you a straight quote.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/gutters1.webp"
            alt="Gutter damage from failed system — Central Texas home"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 bg-brand-900 text-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-xl max-w-[220px] border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-gold-400 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Signs Your Gutters Need Attention</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              {[
                'Water pooling near your foundation after rain',
                'Gutters pulling away from the fascia',
                'Visible rust, cracks, or holes',
                'Water spilling over during heavy rain',
                'Sagging sections or improper slope',
                'Peeling paint or rot on fascia boards',
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-300 text-xs">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-gold-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M8.257 3.099c.765-1.36 2.722-1.36 3.486 0l5.58 9.92c.75 1.334-.213 2.98-1.742 2.98H4.42c-1.53 0-2.493-1.646-1.743-2.98l5.58-9.92zM11 13a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-8a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 002 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                  </svg>
                  {item}
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== SERVICES ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">WHAT WE DO</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-4">
          Gutter Services Lone Ranger Roofing Provides
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Lone Ranger Roofing works with property owners and managers on commercial shingle installations across Temple, Killeen, Belton, Harker Heights, Nolanville, Georgetown, and DFW.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        {gutterServices.map(item => (
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-7 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 flex flex-col gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-accent-600/10 text-accent-600 flex items-center justify-center" set:html={item.icon} />
            <h3 class="font-black text-brand-900 text-lg">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{item.body}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== SEAMLESS VS SECTIONAL ===================== -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">SEAMLESS VS. SECTIONAL</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black text-brand-900 mb-6">
            Seamless vs. Sectional Gutters — What's the Difference?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Traditional sectional gutters come in pre-cut pieces joined together with seams. Those seams are where most gutter problems start — leaking joints, debris buildup, and eventual separation.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Seamless gutters are cut from a single continuous piece of material and custom-fit to your home on-site. No seams means far fewer leak points, better appearance, and longer lifespan. For most homeowners in Temple, Killeen, and across Central Texas and DFW, seamless gutters are the better investment.
          </p>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            {[
              { label: 'Seamless', pros: ['No leak points at seams', 'Custom-fit on-site', 'Better appearance', 'Longer lifespan'] },
              { label: 'Sectional', pros: ['Lower upfront cost', 'Easier DIY repair', 'Still effective when maintained', 'Available in many materials'] },
            ].map(col => (
              <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-100">
                <p class="font-black text-brand-900 text-sm mb-3">{col.label}</p>
                <ul class="space-y-1.5">
                  {col.pros.map(pro => (
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-600 text-xs">
                      <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-accent-600 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                      </svg>
                      {pro}
                    </li>
                  ))}
                </ul>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <img
            src="/gutters4.webp"
            alt="Seamless gutter installation — Central Texas"
            class="w-full h-[480px] object-cover rounded-2xl shadow-xl"
          />
          <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-lg">
            <p class="font-black text-brand-900 text-sm">Seamless Recommended</p>
            <p class="text-accent-600 font-bold text-xs mt-0.5">For Most Central Texas Homes</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===================== HOW IT WORKS ===================== -->
  <section class="relative py-24 bg-brand-900 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/home-gallery1.webp"
        alt="Lone Ranger Roofing gutter installation crew"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-900/95 via-brand-900/80 to-brand-900/95"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-center">

        <div>
          <p class="text-gold-400 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">HOW IT WORKS</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black mb-6">
            Getting New Gutters With Lone Ranger — Simple From Start to Finish
          </h2>
          <p class="text-brand-200 leading-relaxed">
            Most gutter installations are completed efficiently with minimal disruption to your home. Lone Ranger Roofing serves homeowners across Temple, Killeen, and all of Central Texas and DFW.
          </p>
        </div>

